<seg id="1">Islamists receive a life sentence in the UK for planning an attack.</seg>
<seg id="2">On Thursday, the British court issued life sentences to four members of the Islamist cell that called itself Three Musketeers, which planned a terrorist attack against the police and the army.</seg>
