<seg id="23">His recipe does not appear in my show, however," Hruška said, unforgivingly.</seg>
<seg id="24">He's a moron!</seg>
<seg id="25">If you ask me, he's no chef, he's a TV clown.</seg>
<seg id="26">"He's gastronomically illiterate or an imbecile," Pohlreich said of Hruška at one of the presentations.</seg>
