<p>
<seg id="1">Is there a link between Dědka and STAN?</seg>
<seg id="2">From sought-after bride to sales girl.</seg>
<seg id="3">There's a touch of irony involved.</seg>
<seg id="4">With his web project hledameslusny.cz, it seems like the billionaire would essentially like to tell voters that STAN is suffering from a lack of suitable people.</seg>
